===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æɡə|-æɡə]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A South African wild [[donkey]].  The upper parts are reddish brown, becoming paler behind and beneath, with dark stripes on the face, neck, and fore part of the body.  This species is [[extinct]].  Taxonomic name: [[Equus quagga]].

